description: This Hockessin-based truck is the real thing, offering fabulous, from-scratch meals made with fresh, locally-sourced ingredients! From Chickpea Tacos to Rancheros Egg Rolls, these dishes are as unique as they are delicious, wholesome, and filling. You'll find this truck out and about when it's not resting at the Drip Cafe, and our maps will show you just where to find them whenever they tweet their location. For the best eating on the road in Delaware, you've got to try The Brunch Box!
name: The Brunch Box
